    "default_macro_context": {
      "en": "[Missouri presidential context]\nThis template models a generic US presidential race within Missouri (MO). The state's Cook PVI is R+11 based on 2020+2024 two-party share averages. Adjust the macro context to match the cycle and incumbent party you want to simulate.\n\nResponsibility attribution principles:\n- National issues (inflation, foreign policy, immigration) → typically pinned on whichever party holds the White House\n- Missouri state issues → pinned on the in-state governing party",
      "zh-TW": "【Missouri（MO）總統選舉背景】\n本 template 模擬一場 Missouri 內的通用美國總統選舉。該州的 Cook PVI 為 R+11（基於 2020 + 2024 兩黨得票率平均）。請依您想模擬的週期與執政黨調整 macro context。\n\n責任歸屬原則：\n- 全國性議題（通膨、外交、移民）→ 通常歸咎執政黨\n- Missouri 州內議題 → 歸咎州內執政黨"
    },
